name: -M-
description:
Portrait of Mathieu Chedid aka -M-.
-M- is a French rock musician, singer and guitarist.
This portrait means a lot to me and I am so happy to share it with you.
Matthieu Chedid's music has given me a lot of joy and inspiration since my childhood. It was always like fireworks in my heart. And the music videos for the -M- songs nurtured my visual perception of art. During lockdown, his live streams literally saved me. A true artist of the music world
